# Apps started at Hyprland launch
#
# Daemons (waybar, swayosd, hyprpaper, swaync, hypridle, polkit agent,
# cliphist, blueman-applet, dropbox, …) are systemd user services bound to
# graphical-session.target — see ~/.config/systemd/user/. uwsm activates that
# target on session start and stops it on logout, so they come up and go
# down with the compositor. Don't add daemon spawns here.
#
# This file is for one-shot actions that must run after the compositor is
# live but don't have their own systemd lifecycle.

# Restore dark/light mode
exec-once = ~/.local/bin/apply-dark-mode.sh

# Load Hyprland plugins
exec-once = hyprpm reload -n
